<h2 class="bold font-l">YDKJ The Ride: Trapdoor</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Buzz Lipman gets dropped down a trapdoor by Cookie, and the game has to pause while Helen and Cookie argue. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="c20ixm" data-video-descrip="Set during the Spanish Golden Age, this TV &amp;quot;theological difficulties&amp;quot; blurb exhorts its viewer to &amp;quot;please do not adjust your sect.&amp;quot;" data-video-title="Theological Difficulties" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/c20ixm_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/c20ixm.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/WeAreExperiencingTechnicalDifficulties" data-video-tropename="We Are Experiencing Technical Difficulties" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Series/HistoryBites" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/c20ixm.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Theological Dif...</span></p>
</a>
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="dd4pa7" data-video-descrip="Set in Aztec times, the announcer has trouble pronouncing &amp;quot;tenochtechnical.&amp;quot;" data-video-title="Tenochtechnical Difficulties" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/dd4pa7_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/dd4pa7.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/WeAreExperiencingTechnicalDifficulties" data-video-tropename="We Are Experiencing Technical Difficulties" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Series/HistoryBites" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/dd4pa7.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Tenochtechnical...</span></p>
</a>
